## Chat-T2 [G8] SecretaryMessage queue — multiple gates enqueue and dequeue correctly
**Status:** done
**Test File:** `packages/auto-forge-ui/tests/integration/SecretaryMessage.spec.ts`
**Tags:** stack:frontend
**Depends on:** Chat-G1, Relay-D6

```typescript
const inbox = useGateInbox()
inbox.registerGate(gateA)  // becomes active
inbox.registerGate(gateB)  // queued
inbox.registerGate(gateC)  // queued
```

1. Render `<SecretaryMessage gate={inbox.active} />`
2. Assert "+2 more" pill is visible
3. Click pill; assert mini-list shows gateB and gateC
4. Resolve gateA; assert gateB becomes active




